  "author": "XO_OX Designs",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Humpback whale vocal repertoire: long, complex sequences of moans, cries, and whistles that evolve over months. The Conductor arc runs 40 seconds with a slow formant cycle between dark O and deeper U vowels. Vibrato is slow and wide — the whole body resonating. Moderate drama allows partial clusters to form and dissolve like phrases in the whale's song. Each performance is a unique composition.",
